snippet.title: Welcome to Pokémon Playhouse!
snippet.description:
Fun activities and exciting stories are in store for even the youngest Trainers at the Pokémon Playhouse! Designed for children ages 3–5, these activities can be completed without reading or math skills. Visit our official site for more details! http://bit.ly/2wJmEBh

Official site: https://www.pokemon.com
Shop: http://www.pokemoncenter.com 
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/pokemon 
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/pokemon 
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/pokemon 
Tumblr: http://www.pokemon.tumblr.com
